    "title": {
      "rendered": "HOW TO: Curate Nonprofit Videos on YouTube"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Playlists-Nonprofits.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-15459 alignright\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Playlists-Nonprofits-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"YouTube Playlists Nonprofits\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Playlists-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Playlists-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Playlists-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Playlists-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Playlists-Nonprofits.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Nonprofits that do not create a lot of their own video content can still have an engaging YouTube Channel by curating videos relevant to your nonprofit&#8217;s mission and programs. Just because your nonprofit didn&#8217;t create a video doesn&#8217;t mean you can&#8217;t feature it on your channel. By adding videos to &#8220;Playlists&#8221; and then displaying those playlists as &#8220;Sections&#8221; on your channel, your nonprofit can have an engaging YouTube channel that makes a strong first impression. That said, i<em>f your nonprofit does create a lot video content</em>, you should <em>also </em>invest time in organizing and displaying your videos into playlists and sections.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2><strong>Step 1: Create a playlist of at least four videos.</strong></h2>\n<p>Playlists displayed horizontally on your YouTube Channel require a minimum of four videos to fill in the entire section. Research and &#8220;Add to Playlist&#8221; at least four videos that speak to your nonprofit&#8217;s mission and programs. When you add your first video, you will be prompted to create and name your playlist. All videos thereafter can be added by selecting the playlist.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i_Z7whe-YHk\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15449\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-One.png?resize=600%2C442\" alt=\"YouTube Nonprofits One\" width=\"600\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-One.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-One.png?resize=300%2C221&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i1m3iy2xop8&amp;list=PLHSxzMEhsT9MJv15MDKyw9_Llc-6X1Y9Q\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15450\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Two.png?resize=600%2C493\" alt=\"YouTube Nonprofits Two\" width=\"600\" height=\"493\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Two.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Two.png?resize=300%2C246&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Step 2: Add your new playlist as a section to your channel.</h2>\n<p>To display your new playlist(s) on your YouTube Channel, you must add it as section and then use the up or down arrows to feature it on your channel.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-15452\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Three.png?resize=600%2C245\" alt=\"YouTube Nonprofits Three\" width=\"600\" height=\"245\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Three.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Three.png?resize=300%2C122&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15453\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Four.png?resize=600%2C304\" alt=\"YouTube Nonprofits Four\" width=\"600\" height=\"304\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Four.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Four.png?resize=300%2C152&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-15454\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Five.png?resize=600%2C159\" alt=\"YouTube Nonprofits Five\" width=\"600\" height=\"159\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Five.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Five.png?resize=300%2C79&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Step 3: Add your website, icons, and channel banner.</h2>\n<p>Since your nonprofit will be driving more traffic to your YouTube Channel, be sure to add\u00a0your website, icons, and a channel banner to your channel. Since the launch of the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/onechannel\">YouTube One Channel</a> design in March 2013 only a small fraction of nonprofits have updated their YouTube Channel.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/nonprofitorgs\">youtube.com/nonprofitorgs</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-15455\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Seven.png?resize=600%2C346\" alt=\"YouTube Nonprofits Seven\" width=\"600\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Seven.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/YouTube-Nonprofits-Seven.png?resize=300%2C173&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
